snippet.title: The Sims 3 Movie Stuff Trailer -- Part 1
snippet.description: Set the stage with The Sims 3 Movie Stuff and tell more unique stories with décor, furnishings, and clothing inspired by iconic movie genres. Rustle up some new duds, and your Sims will look right at home in some dusty Western saloon. Cast your Sims in The Sims 3 Movie Stuff.
